00:11:58.676 --> 00:12:01.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It all began at the Jetblack.

197
00:12:03.973 --> 00:12:05.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>At the end of the 16th century,</i>

