00:12:08.436 --> 00:12:11.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>in the ruins</i>
<i>at the top of a mountain.</i>

200
00:12:11.272 --> 00:12:13.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>The scientists of the day</i>

201
00:12:13.149 --> 00:12:15.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>classified</i>
<i>the atypical winged skeletons</i>

