205
00:12:22.199 --> 00:12:25.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This was the start of a project
to restore these gods.

206
00:12:27.413 --> 00:12:28.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The King and government realized

207
00:12:28.914 --> 00:12:31.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
they could exploit the project
for political gain...

208
00:12:33.127 --> 00:12:36.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>so in order to refill</i>
<i>the country's depleted coffers,</i>

209
00:12:36.088 --> 00:12:37.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>they solicited donations</i>

210
00:12:37.715 --> 00:12:39.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
