<i>of resurrecting these gods</i>

211
00:12:39.842 --> 00:12:42.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>and built</i>
<i>a huge research facility.</i>

212
00:12:44.221 --> 00:12:45.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>The name of this facility</i>

213
00:12:45.890 --> 00:12:48.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
