<i>Royal Scientific Institute.</i>

214
00:12:50.519 --> 00:12:51.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>The top scientists</i>

215
00:12:51.812 --> 00:12:53.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>and most cutting-edge</i>
<i>technology of the day</i>

216
