00:13:05.993 --> 00:13:08.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>and days spent on trivialities.</i>

221
00:13:09.914 --> 00:13:12.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>With no plan in mind, they</i>
<i>began an inbreeding program,</i>

222
00:13:13.042 --> 00:13:16.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
