<i>called the Promising Ones,</i>

223
00:13:16.420 --> 00:13:19.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>which they later disposed of.</i>

224
00:13:19.381 --> 00:13:23.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>That so-called research was</i>
<i>repeated for several centuries.</i>

225
00:13:24.845 --> 00:13:27.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Eventually rumors
began to circulate,

226
00:13:27.431 --> 00:13:30.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
rumors that the research
would be terminated.

227
00:13:30.351 --> 00:13:31.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
In response to this,

228
00:13:31.727 --> 00:13:34.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
