00:13:37.566 --> 00:13:39.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
designed to manipulate
the balance

231
00:13:39.318 --> 00:13:42.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
