00:13:45.199 --> 00:13:47.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>would be developed</i>
<i>at Jaula Blanca.</i>

234
00:13:49.161 --> 00:13:50.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Thus, the Promising Ones,</i>

235
00:13:50.996 --> 00:13:52.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
