00:14:01.924 --> 00:14:04.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Their work would go on</i>
<i>to have a profound effect.</i>

241
00:14:05.886 --> 00:14:07.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
